snippet.textDisplay: Don't know if anybody will read this comment or not, but as this song started out, I remembered my times as a kid living in Rajasthan and Gujarat and I was like - Wow, this is bring showcased in Coke Studio Pakistan...and the realization came - I, as an Indian, know SO LESS about our neighbors (and probably the same the other way around). We are so similar, but we still know so less about each other. Thank you Coke Studio, for helping me know my neighbors better. Cheers and Love!
